OL,3,CStudent receives Masters after family
OL,4,Cflees Taliban
OL,6,FA student has graduated from the
OL,7,FUniversity of Bristol after her family
OL,8,Ffled religious persecution by the
OL,9,FTaliban.
OL,11,FGurvin Chopra's parents Jaspal and
OL,12,FWaryam left Afghanistan in 2000
OL,13,Fbecause of their Sikh religion.
OL,15,FAlthough neither received any
OL,16,Feducation, and cannot read or write,
OL,17,Fthey encouraged Miss Chopra and her
OL,18,Ftwo younger siblings to work hard at
OL,19,Fschool.
