OL,3,CStudent receives Masters after family
OL,4,Cflees Taliban
OL,6,FMiss Chopra became the first person in
OL,7,Fher family to attend school, and her
OL,8,Fsuccess led to study at university.
OL,10,FThis week, the 23-year-old graduated
OL,11,Ffrom the University of Bristol with
OL,12,Fher master's degree in human rights
OL,13,Flaw and has ambitions of becoming a
OL,14,Flawyer.
OL,16,FGuvin Chopra: 'Access to education can
OL,17,Fbe life-changing'
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
