OL,6,F"For me, as an Afghan woman, the
OL,7,Fsignificance of this day cannot be
OL,8,Foverstated," Miss Chopra said in her
OL,9,Fceremony speech.
OL,11,F"In Afghanistan, women and girls have
OL,12,Fbeen denied the right to an education,
OL,13,Fthe right to be seen and heard.
OL,15,F"These are privileges that I, through
OL,16,Feducation, have been fortunate to
OL,17,Freceive and foster.
OL,26,@pD@LO]
