OL,3,CStudent receives Masters after family
OL,4,Cflees Taliban
OL,6,F"As the only educated woman in my
OL,7,Ffamily, it is an honour and privilege
OL,8,Fto have earned my master's in human
OL,9,Frights law.
OL,11,F"It is through my education that I
OL,12,Fhave been able to see first-hand how
OL,13,Faccess to education can be life-
OL,14,Fchanging, in providing a voice,
OL,15,Ffreedoms and, most importantly,
OL,16,Fchoices.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
