OL,6,F"I always saw education as a way out
OL,7,Fand a way of making myself different
OL,8,Ffrom the women I saw growing up, who
OL,9,Foften didn't work.
OL,11,F"I've found education really
OL,12,Fempowering in breaking away from that,
OL,13,Fdeveloping a voice and helping the
OL,14,Fpeople around me."
