OL,3,CStudent receives Masters after family
OL,4,Cflees Taliban
OL,6,FNow working as an elected officer for
OL,7,FBristol Students' Union, Miss Chopra
OL,8,Fhas also set up a charity, The
OL,9,FBeathard Project, which seeks to
OL,10,Funcover miscarriages of justice to
OL,11,Fposthumously exonerate people who have
OL,12,Fbeen executed for alleged crimes.
OL,14,FAfter finishing her year-long service
OL,15,Fas a students' union officer, Miss
OL,16,FChopra plans to work on her charity
OL,17,Fbefore becoming a human rights lawyer.
